summary: [Image Description: a digital drawing of Dani from The Adventure Zone: Amnesty. She’s a dark skinned vampire, covered in...
body:
[Image Description: a digital drawing of Dani from The Adventure Zone: Amnesty. She’s a dark skinned vampire, covered in freckles. She has long, curly blonde hair, orange eyes, and large ears. She’s wearing a pink beanie, a dark magenta, long sleeved turtleneck shirt, and a blue vest with faux fur lined arm holes. End Description]

Girlfriend Jacket! Girlfriend Jacket! Girlfriend Jacket!

(That’s me not at all subtly saying the jacket is Aubrey’s :p)

Griffin has me so worried about Dani AdventureZone, so I drew her to deal with the stress of waiting for the next episode.

I think I’ve found a design I like most for her, so look forward to more art of her!
